show.description:
She lived a quiet, ordinary life—until a scandal pushed her into the arms of a powerful CEO. When shocking truths about her real identity emerge, her world turns upside down.
Daughter Of The Secret Tycoon is a gripping tale of hidden legacies, forbidden romance, and a rise from overlooked to unstoppable. Watch now!
